# --- Derived data (do NOT re-add) ----------------------------------------
# assets/ held reference images and voice-clone seeds derived from personal
# photos and recordings; *.npy are the particle fields precomputed from those
# images; *.png are renders and frame dumps produced from them. All three are
# reproducible from the code, so they stay out of the repo permanently rather
# than shipping personal source material by accident.
assets/
refs/
*.npy
*.png
*.wav
*.mp3

